        <section class="mb-5">
            <h2 class="h4 text-primary fw-bold">2. How we use your information</h2>
            <p>We use the information we collect for the following purposes:</p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>To operate and maintain our blog:</strong> Your personal information helps us display content and features correctly.</li>
